data.description: Excellent opportunity for one level, low maintenance living in the wonderful Ram Works Condominium. Experience the good life with large living area, 2 nice bedrooms and bath, huge pantry which also serves laundry, new air fryer oven, refrigerator, dishwasher and new fixtures. Ram Works dues cover all exterior maintenance, snow removal, mowing, landscaping etc. so sit back and enjoy the south river flowing nearby. Low utility cost = low cost of living! Call today!
